---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="❓ FAQs - Manuel Gil - Software Developer & Open Source Advocate">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-20">
    <section class="flex items-center justify-center pb-20 pt-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-6xl font-bold text-transparent"
        >
          FAQs
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-20 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">Who can sponsor?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-zinc-200">
          Anyone who wants to support open-source development! Whether you're an individual
          developer, a company, or an organization, your support helps keep these projects alive.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-20 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">Who can sponsor?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-zinc-200">
          Aside from helping sustain open-source tools, sponsors receive <strong
            class="text-zinc-200"
            >recognition, feature prioritization, early access, and direct collaboration
            opportunities</strong
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-20 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">What do sponsors get in return?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-zinc-200">
          You can create an issue on my <strong class="text-zinc-200">GitHub repositories</strong> or
          contact me directly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-20 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">How can I request features or report issues?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-zinc-200">
          Absolutely! Open-source is all about collaboration. Feel free to fork, contribute, and
          submit pull requests.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-20 max-w-5xl">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ManuelGil?tab=repositories"
        class="inline-block text-primary transition-colors hover:text-primary-dark"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        View My GitHub Repositories →
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
